      "title": "amniocentesis<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(n.)</div>",
      "html": "<p>羊水穿刺诊断技术，1958年，现代拉丁语，由 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of amnion \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/amnion\">amnion</a> 和古希腊语的 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">centesis</i> \"刺穿手术\"组成，该词源自希腊语的 Latinized 形式 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">kentesis</i> \"刺穿\"，该词源自希腊语的 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">kentein</i> \"刺\"（源自 PIE 根词 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">*kent-</i> \"刺，戳\"，见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of center \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/center\">center</a>（n.））。</p>"
    },
    {
      "title": "center-field<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(n.)</div>",
      "html": "<p>同样的，1857年在棒球中，“外野的中间三分之一”被称为 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">centerfield</i>，源自于 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of center \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/center\">center</a>（n.）和 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of field \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/field\">field</a>（n.）。相关词汇： <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Center-fielder</i>。</p>"
    }
  ]
